<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.8">
<l>vanta matalaik kuḻāttai valiceytu</l>
<l>tantak kaḷiṟupōl tāṉē viḷaiyāṭum</l>
<l>nantaṉ matalaikku naṉṟu maḻakiya</l>
<l>vunti yiruntavā kāṇīrē yoḷiyiḻai yīrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with bright ornaments, see the quality of the supremely beautiful navel</l>
<l>of the child of Nanda who, like an elephant with a stick,</l>
<l>being aloof toward the swarm of children who come [to play],</l>
<l>plays [by] himself. Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
